cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.DS

This paper is about a framework for automatic differentiation in deep learning, which is a core topic in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.CV (Computer Vision). The paper also discusses optimization methods, which could place it in cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper presents benchmark reports and comparisons, which could also fit in cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
